## ğŸš€ Getting Started (First Time)

### **Prerequisites**
- Docker Desktop installed & running
- Node.js 18+ (for local development)
- Git repository access

### **Quick Start (30 minutes)**
```bash
# 1. Navigate to project
cd "d:\UPENDRA\e-HA Matrix\Dream"

# 2. Start all services
docker-compose up -d

# 3. Install dependencies
cd erp-web && npm install
cd ../erp-api && npm install

# 4. Start development servers
# Terminal 1 - Frontend
cd erp-web && npm run dev    # http://localhost:3000

# Terminal 2 - Backend
cd erp-api && npm run start  # http://localhost:3002

# 5. Test
# Frontend: http://localhost:3000
# Backend: http://localhost:3002/api-docs (Swagger)
# Database: localhost:5432 (postgresql://postgres:postgres@localhost)
